review 4: The access road is quite small, but they offer a parking space. The entrance fee is cheap. I forgot, but ai think it‚Äôs around 15k. And you can get a glass of fresh strawberry juice. And you can pick straight from the farm and bring it home. A nice experience to bring the kids.
review 5: Hidden garden strawberry is a tourist spot where we can pick fresh strawberries straight from the tree. We can reach by motorbike or car because there is already a parking lot available for visitors. When entering the area we will be presented with a garden that is arranged neatly and beautifully in the form of trees that are formed in such a way. For strawberry picking equipment, containers and scissors are also provided here. We can pick strawberries straight from the tree and can choose which strawberry to pick. Besides the strawberry garden and garden, there are also flowers. The place is nice, clean, cool, well maintained and the owner is also friendly. This tourist spot is suitable for families, couples, or anyone who wants to enjoy a quiet natural atmosphere while feeling the freshness of strawberries.
